snippet.title: Teenage Demon Slayer Society - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Teenage Demon Slayer Society is a new turn-based action strategy game where players play as a young Johnny Weston who strategically hacks and slashes his way through hordes of demons. The game is supported by a cast of endearing and humor-filled characters, customizable move sets, style ranks, and more. Teenage Demon Slayer Society is launching in 2024 for PC.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
